2009-09-11  harryvanderwolf

	* [r4383] src/hugin1/hugin/CPDetectorConfig.cpp: [OSX] MacOSX bundle
	  use AutoCustome CP value which was therefore also used (hidden) for
	  other OSses. I disabled this functionality (not removed) due to the
	  fact that MacOSX now adopted TModes AutoCP generator structure. This
	  needs to be dealt with carefully for the 2009.4 release
	* [r4382] src/hugin1/hugin/CPDetectorConfig_default.h: [OSX] MacOSX
	  bundle comes without default AutoCP generator since mid 2008 as we
	  want to prevent any patent conflicts
	* [r4376] src/hugin1/hugin/AutoCtrlPointCreator.cpp,
	  src/hugin1/hugin/CPDetectorConfig.cpp: [OSX] implement TModes
	  autopano structure to MacOSX
	* [r4374] src/hugin1/base_wx/platform.cpp,
	  src/hugin1/base_wx/platform.h: [OSX] prepare OSX for TModes autopano
	  structure

