	* [r3644] src/foreign/vigra/vigra_impex/exr.cxx: Added support for
	  differerent compression algorithms to the Vigra's OpenEXR
	  implementation. Note that Hugin doesn't make use of it yet.
	* [r3643] src/hugin_base/hugin_utils/platform.h: Escape ^ in makefile
	  on Windows. Even thought it's not necessary make interprets \^ as ^
	  which causes problems with folders starting with ^.

