	  Define some variables in the .pto.mk file to give plugin Makefiles
	  hints about
	  what kind of panorama it is: HUGIN_PROJECTION HUGIN_HFOV HUGIN_WIDTH
	  HUGIN_HEIGHT DO_LDR_BLENDED DO_LDR_STACKED_BLENDED DO_HDR_BLENDED.
	  Use them in
	  the example plugin Makefile.

