	  about 1.5MB

2008-09-12  ippei

	* [r3417] mac/Hugin.xcodeproj/project.pbxproj,
	  mac/PutAutoCPtoApplicationSupport.applescript,
	  mac/PutAutopanoSiftToHugin.applescript,
	  mac/matchpoint-complete-mac.sh, platforms/mac/autopano,
	  platforms/mac/autopano/PutAutoCPtoApplicationSupport.applescript,
	  platforms/mac/autopano/PutAutopanoSiftToHugin.applescript,
	  platforms/mac/autopano/apsc_plugin-Info.plist,
