	* [r2951] src/hugin1/hugin/PreviewFrame.cpp: disable toolbar buttons
	  in preview window if they are not applicable
	* [r2950] src/hugin1/hugin/PreviewFrame.cpp: fixed [ 1914694 ] Crash
	  in preview window
	  Additionally, "show all" and "show none" button now update the
	  preview window.

2008-03-14  brunopostle

	* [r2949] src/hugin1/hugin/xrc/data/help_fr_FR/keyboard.html,
	  src/hugin1/hugin/xrc/data/help_fr_FR/manual.html,
	  src/hugin1/hugin/xrc/data/keyboard_pl.html,
