	  used any more, change anyway
	  in attempt to fix bug #1799035

2008-03-14  dangelo

	* [r2948] src/matchpoint/evaluation, src/matchpoint/evaluation/README,
	  src/matchpoint/evaluation/c_eoverlap.cpp,
	  src/matchpoint/evaluation/descdist.cpp,
	  src/matchpoint/evaluation/descperf.m,
	  src/matchpoint/evaluation/descperf_demo.m,
	  src/matchpoint/evaluation/repeatability.m,
	  src/matchpoint/evaluation/repeatability_demo.m: added keypoint
	  detector/descriptor benchmarks from
	  http://www.robots.ox.ac.uk/~vgg/research/affine/index.html
	  Ported to octave. This is a good and comprehensive way to compare
	  different feature detectors/descriptors
	* [r2947] src/CMakeLists.txt, src/matchpoint,
	  src/matchpoint/CMakeLists.txt, src/matchpoint/Descriptor.cpp,
	  src/matchpoint/MatchPoint.cpp, src/matchpoint/edgedetection.hxx:
	  Moved matchpoint into main hugin tree. Fixed crash when computing
	  the descriptors.

2008-03-12  dangelo

	* [r2945] src/hugin_base/hugin_utils/platform.h: Do not quote ~ and \
	  characters on windows (sh from UnxUtils is not a bash shell and uses
	  different meta characters.).
	* [r2944] src/translations/sv.po: updated swedish translation (Ulf
	  Wilhelmson)

