2007-11-01  dangelo

	* [r2517] src/hugin1/hugin/AutoCtrlPointCreator.cpp,
	  src/hugin1/stitch_project/hugin_stitch_project.cpp: fixed error when
	  running autopano kolor
	* [r2516] src/hugin1/base_wx/MyExternalCmdExecDialog.cpp,
	  src/hugin1/base_wx/MyExternalCmdExecDialog.h: wxProcess does not
	  work in wxMSW as it works on Mac and Unix.
	  Output of the child process can't be captured, trying to use
	  a standard windows console to execute, but make.exe executes
	  without console, while autopano does.

2007-10-30  dangelo

	* [r2515] src/hugin1/base_wx/MyExternalCmdExecDialog.cpp: Use
	  wxInputStream::CanRead() instead of wxProcess::IsInputAvailable() to
	  check for output
	  from the child process. IsInputAvailable() uses polling and consumes
	  as much CPU as it can get.
	  Autopano run from within hugin should be twice as fast now.
	  Disabled running the programs in an external xterm.

2007-10-29  dangelo

	* [r2514] src/hugin1/stitch_project/hugin_stitch_project.cpp: Add
	  directory of hugin_stitch_project exectuable to path, required
	  for finding the other binaries such as make etc.
	* [r2513] src/hugin1/hugin/AutoCtrlPointCreator.cpp: fixed autopano
	  kolor call on Win32
	* [r2512] CMakeLists.txt: added more CPack ignore patterns
	* [r2511] src/deghosting/CMakeLists.txt: revert previous change

2007-10-28  dangelo

