2007-10-22  dangelo

	* [r2465] added missing files
	* [r2464] work around a small bug in libpano13 that could creep up
	  when trying to disable the robust estimation during geometric
	  optimisation by removing the "m2" in the m line.
	* [r2463] Added -v and removed -q option
	* [r2462] Changed Console progress display to a simpler one line
	  message, which is hopefully better behaved than the old multiple
	  line message
