2007-10-14  dangelo

	* [r2446] changed options. Geometric optimisation is now optional.
	  Useful if only the straighten function should be applied.
	* [r2445] CMakeLists.txt for the help (not finished yet)
	* [r2444] Added ANN library. It will be required by the future builtin
	  control point matcher
	* [r2443] Install the tools
	* [r2442] added option to render only a subset of the full panorama
	  image. Crop tool in preview window still missing though.
	* [r2441] added option to render only a subset of the full panorama
	  image. Crop tool in preview window still missing though.
	* [r2440] new command line option to specify pixel type of the
	  remapped images. Fixed -i option
