	  src/include/hugin/PreviewFrame.h: use spin button instead of the
	  ugly bitmap arrow buttons for EV control
	  disabled automatic hiding of EV control in HDR mode, doesn't work in
	  wx 2.8
	* [r1984] src/hugin/CPEditorPanel.cpp, src/hugin/CPImageCtrl.cpp,
	  src/include/hugin/CPImageCtrl.h: Added contrast enhancing
	  "magnifiers" for manual control point placement.
	  Points can be moved with the cursor keys by 1/3 pixel.
	  Changing the zoom keeps the selected point in the image centre

