	  src/hugin/xrc/nona_panel.xrc, src/hugin/xrc/vig_corr_dlg.xrc,
	  src/include/hugin/CPEditorPanel.h, src/include/hugin/CPImageCtrl.h,
	  src/include/hugin/ImageCache.h, src/include/hugin/ImagesList.h,
	  src/include/hugin/MainFrame.h, src/include/hugin/MyProgressDialog.h,
	  src/include/hugin/PreviewFrame.h, src/include/hugin/VigCorrDialog.h,
	  src/include/hugin/config_defaults.h: various smaller changes
	* [r1949] src/Panorama/Stitcher.cpp,
	  src/include/PT/RemappedPanoImage.h, src/include/PT/Stitcher.h: added
	  support for new photometric variables and stitching HDR images (via
	  reduce operation)
	* [r1948] src/Panorama/PanoramaMemento.cpp,
	  src/include/PT/PanoramaMemento.h: photometric variables
	* [r1947] src/Panorama/Panorama.cpp, src/include/PT/PanoImage.h,
	  src/include/PT/Panorama.h: new photometric variables
	* [r1946] src/Panorama/PanoImage.cpp: new exposure parameters + code
	  to read exposure value from exif data
	* [r1945] src/Panorama/PTOptimise.cpp: added photometric vars
	* [r1944] src/include/vigra_ext/HDRUtils.h: functors to merge HDR
	  images
	* [r1943] src/Panorama/PhotometricOptimizer.cpp: photometric
	  optimisation functions
	* [r1942] src/hugin/CPImageCtrl.cpp, src/hugin/ImageCache.cpp: changed
	  image cache to provide real HDR images, if required.
	* [r1941] src/hugin/AssistantPanel.cpp: perform photometric aligment
	  when clicking on "Align" button
	* [r1940] src/tools/vig_optimize.cpp: command line tool to estimate
	  photometric parameters
	* [r1939] src/tools/img2vips.cpp: simple test to convert any image to
	  a vips image
	* [r1938] src/include/vigra_ext/Pyramid.h,
	  src/include/vigra_ext/pyramid2.h: use new, super fast reduce
	  operation from enblend
	* [r1937] src/hugin/LensPanel.cpp, src/hugin/xrc/lens_panel-2.5.xrc,
	  src/include/hugin/LensPanel.h: added tab with photometric variables
	* [r1936] src/Panorama/Panorama.vcproj,
