	  src/Panorama/PanoramaMemento.cpp, src/hugin/AssistantPanel.cpp,
	  src/hugin/PanoPanel.cpp, src/hugin/PreviewFrame.cpp,
	  src/nona_gui/nona_gui.cpp: use new projection query function in
	  libpano13, projections are now
	  queried dynamically
	* [r1876] src/hugin/HFOVDialog.cpp: fixed check for HFOV > 179 deg.

