	* [r1875] src/hugin/CPEditorPanel.cpp, src/hugin/CPImageCtrl.cpp,
	  src/include/hugin/CPImageCtrl.h: tried to really work around the
	  problem of the double deletion of
	  control points when pressing "Del"

