	  src/include/PT/PanoImage.h, src/include/hugin/ImageCache.h,
	  src/include/hugin/PreviewFrame.h, src/include/hugin/PreviewPanel.h:
	  preview speedup: only remap images if required.
	  Correctly keep selected images when moving or removing images
	* [r1666] src/hugin/CPEditorPanel.cpp, src/hugin/ImageCache.cpp,
	  src/hugin/MainFrame.cpp, src/include/hugin/ImageCache.h,
	  src/include/vigra_ext/Correlation.h, src/include/vigra_ext/utils.h:
	  improved image cache, keep most recently used images, lower memory
	  usage during fine tuning

