2006-06-08  dangelo

	* [r1620] configure.ac: previous change always disabled hugin and
	  nona_gui
	* [r1619] configure.ac, src/Makefile.am: added --disable-gui configure
	  option, for people that just want to build
	  fulla and nona. This does not require wxWidgets.
	* [r1618] src/tools/fulla.cpp: bugfix: gamma setting doesn't enforce
	  PTLens lookup

2006-06-07  dangelo

	* [r1617] src/Panorama/SpaceTransform.cpp,
	  src/include/PT/SpaceTransform.h, src/tools/fulla.cpp: fulla: minor
	  speedup by incoporating scaling into first distortion
	  correction.

2006-06-04  dangelo

	* [r1616] src/tools/fulla.cpp, src/tools/fulla.vcproj: fulla: fixed
	  radial vignetting correction, added gamma option
	* [r1615] src/Panorama/SpaceTransform.cpp, src/build_msvc/Hugin.sln,
	  src/hugin/hugin.vcproj, src/include/PT/SpaceTransform.h,
	  src/tools/fulla.cpp, src/tools/fulla.vcproj: fulla:
	  * improved merging of green and (red,blue) correction coefficients.
	  The previous scheme was an approximation and could lead to
	  errors of 0.2 pixels in a 6 megapixel image.
	  * added option to output unscaled output with black borders.
	* [r1614] src/include/PT/SpaceTransform.h, src/tools/fulla.cpp: fixed
	  serious bug in fulla that lead to wrong tca correction coefficients
	  being used. Now TCA & distortion correction should work at the same
	  time.
	* [r1613] ChangeLog: updated changelog

