	  estimation
	* [r1476] src/hugin/po/POTFILES.in, src/hugin/po/ca_ES.po,
	  src/hugin/po/de.po, src/hugin/po/fr.po, src/hugin/po/hu.po,
	  src/hugin/po/hugin.pot, src/hugin/po/it.po, src/hugin/po/ja.po,
	  src/hugin/po/nl.po, src/hugin/po/pl.po, src/hugin/po/pt_BR.po,
	  src/hugin/po/ru.po, src/hugin/po/zh_CN.po: added new strings to
	  translation

2006-02-05  dangelo

	* [r1475] src/hugin/RunOptimizerFrame.cpp,
	  src/include/hugin/RunOptimizerFrame.h: use synchronous mode for
	  PTOptimizer on MacOSX. There will be no graphical progress output
	  during optimisation. I hope this will avoid the crashes some people
	  have observed.
	* [r1474] src/hugin/VigCorrDialog.cpp: honor active images (can be
	  used to exclude some images from the estimation, by deselecting them
	  in the Preview panel)
	* [r1473] src/hugin/PanoPanel.cpp: enabled PTStitcher on MAC, since
	  PTMender is available
	* [r1472] src/hugin/Plot2D.cpp: fixed enless loop if x or y range = 0
	* [r1471] src/include/vigra_ext/RansacParameterEstimator.h: part of
	  the ransac classes.. forgot to add
	* [r1470] doc/nona.txt: document coordinate image creation
	* [r1469] AUTHORS: the ransac algorithm was implemented by Ziv Yaniv
	* [r1468] src/build_msvc/Hugin.sln,
	  src/build_msvc/hugin_msvc_install.bat,
	  src/build_msvc/hugin_msvc_install_win98.bat: updated msvc build
	  scripts
	* [r1467] src/include/common/math.h: added some utility functions
	* [r1466] src/include/vigra_ext/ImageTransforms.h,
	  src/include/vigra_ext/Interpolators.h,
	  src/include/vigra_ext/ROIImage.h,
