2005-06-09  ippei

	* [r1285] src/hugin/CPEditorPanel.cpp: widen the first column 10 pixel
	  as it was smaller than enough for 2 digits on Mac.
	* [r1284] mac/autopano-complete-mac.sh,
	  src/hugin/AutoCtrlPointCreator.cpp: Mac: Dropping support for
	  Internal autopano-sift script + External autopano-sift executables.
	  Now the options are 1. both internal or 2. specifying working script
	  that already has the path of autopano-sift set with either paths
	  starting with / or ~/, or through system's search path. In other
	  words, users have to choose either "dead easy but may not work", or
	  "should work if you set up properly".

