	* [r1272] src/hugin/xrc/pano_panel-2.5.xrc: Made layout more
	  consistent, by moving h/vfov and projection type to the top,
	  kind of "important" panorama options. I believe the layout is kind
	  of
	  conistent and should not be changed substatially before 0.5.
	  Also made some small changes to the spacing.
	* [r1271] src/hugin/xrc/nona_panel.xrc: added space before compression
	  selection spinbox
	* [r1270] src/hugin/xrc/ptstitcher_panel.xrc: made ptstitcher panel
	  look similar to nona panel

2005-06-08  ippei

	* [r1269] src/hugin/xrc/nona_panel.xrc: Moving enblend click box to
	  output file section. This is a minimum change to fix the strange
	  grouping of this panel, but if not appropriate, probably it's a good
	  idea to reverse this change.
	* [r1268] src/hugin/xrc/pano_panel-2.5.xrc: Putting field of view out
	  from the custom options and moving projection setting into this
	  section. This is a minimum change to fix the strange grouping of
	  this panel, but if not appropriate, probably it's a good idea to
	  reverse this change.
	* [r1267] src/hugin/xrc/cp_editor_panel-2.5.xrc,
	  src/hugin/xrc/lens_panel-2.5.xrc: Removing labels seems meaningless.
	* [r1266] src/hugin/xrc/cp_editor_panel-2.5.xrc: fixing min size of
	  the tabs which was smaller than Mac's widget size.
	* [r1265] src/hugin/xrc/lens_panel-2.5.xrc: Spacing improvements
	* [r1264] src/hugin/xrc/cp_editor_panel-2.5.xrc: Changed the sizer
	  order from horizontal under vertical to vertical under horizontal,
	  and moved add and delete button so that the window can get smaller
	  without scrolls than before. Add button also became more accessible,
	  and everything you use when adding points manually got together in
	  the right hand side.
	* [r1263] src/hugin/xrc/cp_editor_panel-2.5.xrc,
	  src/hugin/xrc/cp_editor_panel.xrc: Back ground colour of some
	  widgets that look strange on Mac. I hope I'm not breaking anything
	  on other platforms.
	* [r1262] src/hugin/xrc/nona_panel.xrc,
	  src/hugin/xrc/pano_panel-2.5.xrc: Balanced the spacing a little bit.
	  It's not excellent yet, but I stop here for now.
	* [r1261] src/hugin/xrc/nona_panel.xrc,
	  src/hugin/xrc/pano_panel-2.5.xrc: Spacing fix for below the small
	  lables
	* [r1260] src/hugin/xrc/nona_panel.xrc,
