	* [r924] src/Panorama/PanoToolsInterface.cpp,
	  src/hugin/CPEditorPanel.cpp, src/hugin/CPImageCtrl.cpp,
	  src/hugin/CPListFrame.cpp, src/hugin/ImagesPanel.cpp,
