2004-09-08  dangelo

	* [r708] src/tools/zhang_undistort.cpp: simple test tool to undistort
	  images according to the zhang camera model.
	  an opensource calibration tool is available from
	  http://www.loper.org/~matt/CamChecker/CamChecker_docs/html/index.html
	* [r707] src/hugin/MainFrame.cpp, src/hugin/PreviewFrame.cpp,
	  src/hugin/huginApp.cpp, src/include/PT/ImageGraph.h,
	  src/nona_gui/nona_gui.cpp: Fixes for Mac OSX compilation. Thanks to
	  Ippei UKAI for the activity on the Mac
	* [r706] src/hugin/huginApp.cpp: minor change
	* [r705] src/Makefile: do not build PanoImage by default
	* [r704] src/hugin/Makefile, src/hugin/NonaStitcherPanel.cpp,
	  src/include/PT/Stitcher.h, src/tests/Makefile, src/tools/Makefile:
	  minor changes (DEBUG output etc.)
	* [r703] src/hugin/CPFineTuneFrame.cpp,
	  src/hugin/CPZoomDisplayPanel.cpp,
	  src/include/hugin/CPFineTuneFrame.h,
	  src/include/hugin/CPZoomDisplayPanel.h: added window to display the
	  magnified and perspetive corrected control points.
	  DISABLED, because of a bug in the orientation estimation.
	* [r702] src/tests/vigra_ext.cpp: added some test that compare the two
	  correlation routines
	* [r701] src/makefiles/rules.mk: abort building after a compiler error
	  has occured.
	* [r700] src/hugin/RunOptimizerFrame.cpp,
	  src/hugin/RunStitcherFrame.cpp: better output parsing of PTStitcher
	  and PTOptimizer (optimizing progress works properly with newer Pano
	  Tools library)
	* [r699] src/hugin/PanoPanel.cpp: removed stupid cut'n'paste error
	  that created the nona output files before the stitching.
	  This broke nona stitching if the correct file extension was
	  specified.
	* [r698] src/hugin/CPEditorPanel.cpp, src/hugin/CPImageCtrl.cpp,
	  src/hugin/MainFrame.cpp, src/include/hugin/CPEditorPanel.h,
	  src/include/hugin/CPImageCtrl.h, src/include/panoinc_WX.h,
	  src/include/vigra_ext/Correlation.h: added new correlation function
	  that will also search for rotated patches.
	  it must be enabled in the config file (or registry), by setting
	  CPEditorPanel/RotationSearch = 1
	  the angle interval that should be tried can be specified with
	  
	  CPEditorPanel/RotationStartAngle
	  CPEditorPanel/RotationStopAngle
	  CPEditorPanel/RotationSteps
	* [r697] src/Panorama/Panorama.cpp: fixed control point parsing bug
	  with newer pano12.dll's
	* [r696] src/common/utils.cpp: fixed error when the path to an output
	  file contained a .

2004-08-30  dangelo

	* [r695] src/hugin/MainFrame.cpp: fix endless loop on removing images,
	  looks like an unsigned int can get
	  negative with the gcc 3.3 under linux, that is (! (uint >= 0)) can
	  become
	  true..
	* [r694] src/hugin/LensPanel.cpp: fixed a typo (file dialog was called
	  save instead of load)

