	  Added a proof-of-concept "panorama druid" feature in the preview
	  frame.
	  This feature watches as you work, and updates itself to advise you
	  on any
	  steps or parameters you may have forgotten. Currently very limited,
	  but
	  will be extending this to add more smarts in the future. Comments
	  welcome.

