2003-10-10  dangelo

	* [r346] src/hugin/ImagesPanel.cpp, src/hugin/LensPanel.cpp,
	  src/hugin/Makefile, src/hugin/PanoPanel.cpp,
	  src/hugin/TextKillFocusHandler.cpp, src/hugin/xrc/pano_panel.xrc,
	  src/include/hugin/ImagesPanel.h, src/include/hugin/LensPanel.h,
	  src/include/hugin/PanoPanel.h,
	  src/include/hugin/TextKillFocusHandler.h, src/makefile.g95: -
	  updates to text fields are applied now on enter and whenever
	  the focus leaves the textcontrol.
	  
	  A custom event handler TextKillFocusHandler converts KILL_FOCUS
	  events
	  to TEXT_ENTER events. It has to be added (and removed) to every
	  wxTextCtrl
	* [r345] src/hugin/xrc/cp_editor_panel.xrc: - moved next/prev button
	  close to the tab bar
	* [r344] AUTHORS, src/hugin/CPEditorPanel.cpp,
	  src/hugin/CPImageCtrl.cpp, src/hugin/xrc/cp_editor_panel.xrc,
