	  src/hugin/MainFrame.cpp, src/include/hugin/ImagesPanel.h: - use
	  DEBUG_TRACE
	  - ImagesPanel uses the specified panorama object and does not
	  create its own.
	  - use add/removeObserver. subcontrols add/remove themself, MainFrame
	  is no longer responsible for forwarding the panoramaChanged()
	  function calls.
	* [r161] src/include/common/utils.h: added printing of function name
	  to DEBUG_* macros. uses C99 compatible __func__
	  instead of the GNU specific __FUNCTION__ macro
	* [r160] src/Panorama/Panorama.cpp, src/include/PT/Panorama.h: -
	  replaced setObserver() with addObserver() and removeObserver()
	  many classes can register themself as observers now.
